{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是不是因为你心里已有了我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我的确应该知道你能认得出我来的，因为，你就算化成了灰，我也认得出你。","tone":"温柔","chapter":30,"line_start":114,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"但是你却希望我认不出你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":122,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你进去看看，就知道是为什么了。","tone":"犹豫","chapter":30,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你不进去？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我可以在外面等着。","tone":"平静","chapter":30,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"为什么要在外面等？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为你进去了之后，一定也希望我在外面等着。","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":136,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"不管你是谁，你既然在等我，就该知道我是谁。","tone":"沉声","chapter":30,"line_start":186,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"我并不是个凶恶的人，所以你根本不必怕我。","tone":"平静","chapter":30,"line_start":192,"line_end":192}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":null,"text":"我是小叶。难道你听不出我的声音？","tone":"焦急","chapter":30,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你已知道屋子里的人是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":246,"line_end":248},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你为什么不点起灯来？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":30,"line_start":250,"line_end":250},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我又不在屋子里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":252,"line_end":252},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你没有火折子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":256,"line_end":256},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"既然有，为什么刚才不给我？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":30,"line_start":258,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"火……火……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":30,"line_start":270,"line_end":274},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"火……火……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":30,"line_start":274,"line_end":274}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":301,"line_end":400,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你现在是不是已明白，刚才我为什么不肯给你火折子？","tone":"苦笑","chapter":30,"line_start":282,"line_end":284},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"她是从火窟中逃出来的，她受的惊骇太大，可是……可是我实在想不到，她竟已连你都不认得。","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":288,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你是在哪里找到她的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":292,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"就在这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"几时找到的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"她逃出火窟后，想必就已躲到这里来，可是我直到今天晚上才找到她。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":298,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我知道你看见她这样子，一定会很难受，可是我又不能不带你来。","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":302,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我本不想让你知道是我带你来的，因为……因为……","tone":"犹豫","chapter":30,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"因为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我也不知道究竟为了什么，也许是因为我不愿让你为了这件事而感激我，也许是因为我害怕。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":30,"line_start":312,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"害怕？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"她变成这样子，我也有责任，我怕你怪我，恨我……我更怕你见了她之后，会从此不理我。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":30,"line_start":318,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"但你却还是带我来了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"所以我自己也不知道自己究竟是在做什么？","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你猜我现在想干什么？","tone":"微笑","chapter":30,"line_start":330,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我想去找个地方睡一觉。","tone":"平静","chapter":30,"line_start":336,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"现在你想去睡觉？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":30,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"明天中午我还有事，我一定要养足精神。","tone":"认真","chapter":30,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你……你睡得着？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":30,"line_start":342,"line_end":342},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我为什么睡不着？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"可是丁灵琳……","tone":"担心","chapter":30,"line_start":346,"line_end":346},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"不管怎么样，我们现在总算已找到了她，别的事都可以等到以后再说。","tone":"平静","chapter":30,"line_start":348,"line_end":350},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"她这样子你能放心得下？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":352,"line_end":352},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"有金钱帮的帮主在这里保护她，我还有什么不放心的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":30,"line_start":354,"line_end":356},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"看来就算有天大的烦恼，你也能一下子就抛开。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":30,"line_start":362,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"这世上本没有什么值得烦恼的事。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":30,"line_start":366,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你实在是个很有福气的人。","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"明天中午，你有什么事要做？","tone":"好奇","chapter":30,"line_start":372,"line_end":372},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我有个约会。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"什么约会。","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"孤峰和多尔甲约好了明天中午在延平门相见。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"这是他们的约会，你……","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"现在多尔甲既然已死了，这约会就变成我的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":382,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你想乘此机会，找出孤峰来？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"嗯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":388,"line_end":388},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"每天正午，出入延平门的人也不知有多少，你怎么知道谁是孤峰？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":390,"line_end":392},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我总有法子找到的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":30,"line_start":394,"line_end":394},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"什么法子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":396,"line_end":396},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"现在连我自己也不知道，可是到时候我就能想出来。","tone":"微笑","chapter":30,"line_start":398,"line_end":400}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_gu_feng","name":"孤峰","alias":[],"identity":"神秘人物","faction":"无门派","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"与多尔甲有约的神秘人物","personality":{"traits":["神秘","隐秘","谨慎","老练","不可捉摸"],"speech_style":"不详","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_duo_er_jia","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"有约在先"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[30],"source_refs":[{"chapter":30,"line_start":378,"line_end":378,"text":"孤峰和多尔甲约好了明天中午在延平门相见"}]},{"id":"char_duo_er_jia","name":"多尔甲","alias":[],"identity":"已故人物","faction":"无门派","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"已死的人物，原与孤峰有约","personality":{"traits":["已故","曾经活跃","与孤峰有约","身份不明","曾参与秘密行动"],"speech_style":"不详","temperament":"不详"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_gu_feng","type":"合作者","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"已死"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[30],"source_refs":[{"chapter":30,"line_start":378,"line_end":378,"text":"孤峰和多尔甲约好了明天中午在延平门相见"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_yan_ping_men","name":"延平门","region":"长安","one_line":"长安城门之一，孤峰与多尔甲约定见面之处","source_refs":[{"chapter":30,"line_start":378,"line_end":378,"text":"孤峰和多尔甲约好了明天中午在延平门相见"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":401,"line_end":482,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你自己去睡觉，却要我替你在这里保护她？","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":408,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":null,"text":"现在我才知道他为什么总是没有烦恼了，因为他总是能将他的烦恼送给别人的。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":30,"line_start":414,"line_end":416},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"早！","tone":"微笑","chapter":30,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"现在好像已不早了。","tone":"调侃","chapter":30,"line_start":432,"line_end":432},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"虽然不早，也不太晚。","tone":"微笑","chapter":30,"line_start":434,"line_end":434},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"看来你一定睡得很熟。","tone":"调侃","chapter":30,"line_start":436,"line_end":436},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"睡得简直就像死人一样。","tone":"大笑","chapter":30,"line_start":438,"line_end":438},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"我实在想不到你居然真的能睡着。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":30,"line_start":440,"line_end":440},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我想睡时，就算天塌下来，我也照睡不误。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":30,"line_start":442,"line_end":442},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"她什么时候睡了。","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":446,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"天亮了才睡。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":448,"line_end":448},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"看来她好像也吃了点东西。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"吃了一碗炖鸡面，吃完了才肯睡。","tone":"陈述","chapter":30,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"幸好她总算睡了，否则我连门都进不来。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":30,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":458,"line_end":458},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"无论谁一走进来，她就拿着刀要杀人。","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"不管怎么样，能吃得下，睡得着，总是好事。","tone":"微笑","chapter":30,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只可惜我吃也吃不下，睡也睡不着，我实在没有你们这么好的福气。","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":464,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你想出法子来没有？","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":468,"line_end":468},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我还没有开始想。","tone":"平静","chapter":30,"line_start":470,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你准备什么时候才开始想。","tone":"疑问","chapter":30,"line_start":472,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"到了城门再想。","tone":"平静","chapter":30,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你倒是一点也不着急。","tone":"无奈","chapter":30,"line_start":476,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"船到桥头自然直，这句话我一直都很相信。","tone":"微笑